  <h2>What you're submitting today</h2>
  <p class="sub">One Chennai-area erosion example. Be specific.</p>
  <div class="submission-callout">
    <div class="label">Erosion example — screenshot + interpretation</div>
    <p>One Google Earth screenshot (or a Block-2 walk photo if you went Path C). Two sentences. Sentence one names the erosion agent you're claiming is dominant. Sentence two cites the visible evidence. "I see erosion at Marina Beach" is too generic — "I see longshore drift carrying sand southward along the Marina, evidenced by the sediment accumulation on the south side of the breakwater" is the move.</p>
